{"tid":759279,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple 為日本水災災民提供免費維修","createTime":"2018-07-28T12:44:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T15:48:31.000Z","uid":141151,"like":58,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"46de9ae9c4f82e50cad717d2767e08a265991840","tid":759279,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:44:22.000Z","msg":"Apple 為日本水災災民提供免費維修<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/07/28/japan-flood-apple-offer-free-repair/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2Fjapan-flood-apple-offer-free-repair%2Flife-tech%2F&d=dy%2FRrdHMVvVmQJii9%2F0beh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=4b9e5349\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/07/28/japan-flood-apple-offer-free-repair/life-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\n早前日本西部受暴雨影響，引發廣泛地區嚴重水浸，至少 209 人因此失去寶貴性命，還未計算個別失蹤人口。有不少房屋因此被淹浸，當中受災最嚴重的則是廣島縣和岡山縣。房屋被破壞，屋內的數碼產品亦無從倖免，幸好 Apple 宣佈提供免費維修服務。<br />\n<br />\n日本傳媒報導指，Apple 宣佈向所有受今次水災影響的用戶提供免費維修服務，用戶可以將有問題的裝置帶到當地 Apple 專門店，亦可以透過郵寄方式寄出。雖然 Apple 暫時未有在官方網站提供進一步資料，但就設立了熱線讓受影響的用戶致電查詢。Apple 今次維修的產品包括 Mac 電腦、iPhone、iPad、iPod、Apple Watch，還有 Apple 和 Beats 的配件，Appl 無法確保一定能夠將產品修好，但表示會盡力提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n今次免費維修服務將會由即日起提供，限期至 9 月底。"},{"pid":"c5abaa22275e78fa7c66f5c36b709d42fd71d4e9","tid":759279,"uid":72979,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:45:42.000Z","msg":"良心企業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d0fbcf9f52ff6e955640bacf9e2585e1093d88","tid":759279,"uid":50060,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:47:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一堆番新機"},{"pid":"a43306099f6cbcbc4a3d131b83f0b829797316ed","tid":759279,"uid":91664,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:50:33.000Z","msg":"下部一定買iPhone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d4905286467e8e1801c317c55cc5ac7e940450","tid":759